          <div class="letter-card" data-letter-content="I">
            <div class="letter-header">
              <span class="letter-big">I</span>
              <div>
                <h3>Immunology</h3>
                <p>
                  Antibodies and immune cells recognizing and clearing pathogens.
                  This can include antibody–antigen binding or immune cells chasing invaders.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="video-single">
              <video src="immunology-clip.mp4" autoplay loop muted playsinline></video>
