              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- C – Cell Culture -->
          <div class="letter-card" data-letter-content="C">
            <div class="letter-header">
              <span class="letter-big">C</span>
              <div>
                <h3>Cell Culture</h3>
                <p>
                  Growing cells in flasks or dishes under controlled conditions
                  to study growth, test drugs, or produce biological products.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="video-single">
              <video src="cell-culture-clip.mp4" autoplay loop muted playsinline></video>
