              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- H – Hemoglobin -->
          <div class="letter-card" data-letter-content="H">
            <div class="letter-header">
              <span class="letter-big">H</span>
              <div>
                <h3>Hemoglobin</h3>
                <p>
                  Hemoglobin inside red blood cells carries oxygen throughout the body.
                  Its structure and oxygen-binding are key in physiology.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="video-single">
